{/* Project Section */}

Equipmaster

An addon to automate gear equipping in the game.
To use it simply open your character frame and
click the Button with the arrow facing down.
The addon will scan your bags and equip the highest
item level gear you can use.

BuildaPCVR

VRBuildaPC is a VR PC building simulator
designed to provide users with a comprehensive
and engaging learning experience in assembling
a computer. Users will step into a virtual
workshop equipped with lifelike components,
tools, and step-by-step guides to simulate
the process of building a PC from scratch.

Bok Choy

In the adventure game Bok Choy Adventure,
players will follow Amara, a young adventurer
lost on a mysterious and visually stunning island
after a deadly shipwreck. The game delivers a truly
engaging experience, immersing players in a
rich and dynamic world filled with exciting < br /> secrets waiting to be revealed.

Neon Nights

The game is a cyberpunk RPG set in a dystopian
future where players take on the role of a
street-wise hacker trying to survive in a
world of corrupt corporations, ruthless gangs,
and high-tech weaponry. The game's UI should be
designed to create a sense of urban grittiness
and high-tech innovation, with a sleek and
stylized design.

EcoConnect

EcoConnect is a mobile app designed to
encourage and facilitate sustainable living by
connecting individuals within local communities.
The app aims to promote eco-friendly practices.
